Document: WorldEnvironment  
Path: godot/classes/class_worldenvironment.rst  
Summary: Describes the camera_attributes, compositor, and environment properties of the WorldEnvironment class.  

Property: camera_attributes (CameraAttributes): The default CameraAttributes resource to use if none set on the Camera3D. Methods: set_camera_attributes(value: CameraAttributes), get_camera_attributes() → CameraAttributes.  
Property: compositor (Compositor): The default Compositor resource to use if none set on the Camera3D. Methods: set_compositor(value: Compositor), get_compositor() → Compositor.  
Property: environment (Environment): The Environment resource used by this WorldEnvironment, defining the default properties. Methods: set_environment(value: Environment), get_environment() → Environment.